title: Regulating Oxygen Vacancy and Coordination Environment of Manganese Dioxides for Enhanced High-Mass-Loading Energy Storage
content:
Energy Environ. Sci., 2024, Accepted Manuscript
DOI: 10.1039/D4EE00949E, Paper
Zhongyou Peng, Yuting Huang, Alexander G. Bannov, Shulong Li, Ling Tang, Licheng Tan, Yiwang Chen
Although manganese oxides (MnO2) have been extensively studied for energy storage, further applications are limited due to its sluggish electron/ion transfer kinetics and insufficient active sites, especially under high-mass loading...
